Privacy Policy – AniByte!
We value your privacy and want to ensure that you are aware of how we handle your data during your gaming experience.
Data Collection:
While using the game, we collect strictly necessary information for the game’s functionality, such as your in-game progress, configuration preferences, and gameplay statistics.
We do not collect or store personally identifiable information, such as names, email addresses, or contact information.
Use of Data:
The data collected is used exclusively to enhance your gaming experience and for internal analysis purposes. We do not share this data with third parties.
Data Security:
We have implemented appropriate security measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
Cookies:
We do not use cookies to track your activity outside of the game.
Changes to the Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to make changes to this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be reflected on this page.
Contact:
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at pkdev02@gmail.com.
By continuing to play our games, you agree to this Privacy Policy.
Thank you for choosing our game and trusting us with your data. Enjoy!